{"product_id":"white-oudh-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"White Oudh Attar (Roll On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol Free","description":"\u003cp\u003e Discover the smooth, elegant and modern fragrance of White Oudh Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYe attar traditional oud ka soft aur refined version hai, jo heavy nahi lagta aur classy feel deta hai.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhite Oudh un logon ke liye perfect hai jo oud pasand karte hain but light aur balanced fragrance chahte hain.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDaily wear, office, namaz aur special occasions sab ke liye suitable hai.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: Soft Oud, Woody \u0026amp; Elegant\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong Lasting \u0026amp; Smooth\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium glass roll-on bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for men \u0026amp; women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose White Oudh\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOud ki richness, bina heavy feel ke\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFresh, classy aur modern fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHeadache-free aur skin-friendly\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium packaging, gifting ke liye bhi perfect\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNeck, wrist ya pulse points par halka sa apply karein aur elegant oud fragrance enjoy karein.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50472865857783,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/79AA7FEA-C125-420B-91F0-3D0683DBE3F3.png?v=1777870289","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/white-oudh-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","provider":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","version":"1.0","type"